    <section id="id6030274">
      <title>South Africa</title>
      <para id="id5809262">Pack your suitcases, because we are going to travel through South Africa. South Africa is the most southerly country of Africa and is surrounded by the Atlantic Ocean and the Indian Ocean. South Africa is divided into nine provinces.</para>
      <figure id="id5788195">
        <media id="id5788195_media" alt="">
          <image mime-type="image/jpg" src="../../media/graphics1-5119.jpg" id="id5788195__onlineimage" height="530" width="625"/>
        </media>
      </figure>
      <list id="id7452407" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Colour the province where you live red.</item>
        <item>Colour each province in a different colour.</item>
        <item>What is the capital of your province? _______________</item>
      </list>
    </section>
    <section id="id1169576235674">
      <title>Discuss in groups:</title>
      <list id="id8666069" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Each group must collect information on one of the cities.</item>
        <item>Make a poster of all the places of interest in your city.</item>
        <item>Now go on an imaginary tour with your group to each city.</item>
        <item>Visit each of the other cities and see how many facts you can remember.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id2144473">Write down the name of your province.</para>
      <para id="id8664341">Answer the following questions. Ask Mum or Dad to help you.</para>
      <list id="id1410391" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
        <item>Where were you born?</item>
        <item>How long have you been living / did you live in this town or city?</item>
        <item>Where do you live now?</item>
        <item>What makes your town / city special?</item>
        <item>Where would you take me if I were to come and visit you?</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id7021416"/>
      <list id="id1923934" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Connect the town / city with the correct picture:</item>
        <item>Find out more about one of the historical buildings and inform the class.</item>
      </list>
      <figure id="id6690716">
        <media id="id6690716_media" alt="">
          <image mime-type="image/jpg" src="../../media/graphics2-589e.jpg" id="id6690716__onlineimage" height="551" width="551"/>
        </media>
      </figure>
    </section>
