      <list id="id4012412" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Display a map of S.A. in the class.</item>
        <item>Have a general class discussion as an introduction and point out the various continents on a world map or a globe to ensure that learners know where S.A. is.</item>
        <item>Make available sources dealing with different cities.</item>
        <item>Learners can do an informal oral on an interesting town.</item>
